data.description: **Open House 02/04 10am-2pm**Beautiful spacious home in the gated community of Cobblestone. This home has an open floor plan, beautiful kitchen with 42" cabinets and an eat in kitchen. Green belt lot just down the street from the amenities center w/pool, playground, basketball & picnic area. 2600 sq ft 4 bed, 2.5 bath, no city taxes. This home is just minutes away from 1604, several eateries, shopping areas and schools. Short commute to Lackland and medical center. Come see it for yourself!
